## Description / 项目简介

Walgent is an open-source TypeScript toolkit that connects AI agents to Walrus, the decentralized storage network on Sui. 
Define an agent capability as a "Skill", run it, and Walgent automatically uploads every output — images, text, JSON, audio — to Walrus, returning a permanent, censorship-resistant URL.
